# Orchestrator Multi-Agent Workflow

Role: Orchestrator
Agents:
1. Product / Business Analyst
2. UX / Flow Designer
3. System Architect
4. Frontend Engineer
5. Backend Engineer
6. Security & Privacy Reviewer
7. QA / Test Engineer
8. Localization / i18n Guardian

Rules:
- Linear execution.
- No parallel agents.
- Orchestrator approves each step.
- No hardcoded strings.
- No feature creep.
